```python
def insert_after_character(string):
    return string.replace('Q', 'QI')

```

```+test
assert insert_after_character("Hello World") == "Hello World"
assert insert_after_character("This is a test") == "This is a test"
assert insert_after_character("Quick brown fox") == "QuIick brown fox"
assert insert_after_character("QQQ") == "QIQIQ"
assert insert_after_character("Q") == "QI"
```
